LIF - Logical interface (It is an IP Address)
Own port, own node, protocols, roles
When creating LIF assign to a particular port.
Roles: Node Management, Data, Intercluster

SAN FC - A LIF is nothing but WWPN 

Note: For Each SVM we need two Data LIFs(node1 & node2) for Data redundancy.

Network --> Network Interfaces --> Create --> 

To enable DNS on Each LIF to avoid the connectivity issue (Modify network on in CLI)
::> network interface modify -lif <LIF-Name> -vserver <vserver-name> dns zone <DNS Name>
